<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>후기 남기기</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/style.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page narrow">
    <header class="sub-hero">
      <h1>후기 남기기</h1>
      <p>방문 후기나 사용 경험을 자유롭게 남겨주세요.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="top-actions">
      <a class="btn" href="/">목록으로</a>
    </div>

    <% if (error) { %>
      <p class="error-text"><%= error %></p>
    <% } %>

    <form method="post" action="/write" class="form-card">
      <label class="label">이름 또는 닉네임</label>
      <input type="text" name="author_name" placeholder="예: 홍길동 / 만족한 고객" />

      <label class="label">제목</label>
      <input type="text" name="title" placeholder="제목을 입력하세요" required />

      <label class="label">내용</label>
      <textarea name="content" placeholder="후기 내용을 입력하세요" required></textarea>

      <button type="submit" class="btn primary full">등록하기</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
